##############################################################################
Build and install everything:

git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
make install

Options to cmake:
-DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/install_prefix
    Change the install prefix from the default /usr/local

-DNOPGLD=1
    Don't build pgld

-DNOPGLCMD=1
    Don't build pglcmd

-DNOPGLGUI=1
    Don't build pgl-gui

-DNODUBS=1
    For pgld only
    No DBus support (Auto-detect otherwise)

-DLOWMEM=1
    For pgld only
    Enable LOWMEM support for devices like routers etc
    This disables DBus

##############################################################################
Building only pgld:

Required packages:
    libnfnetlink-dev
    libnfnetlink0
    libnetfilter-queue-dev
    libnetfilter-queue1

Recommended packages:
    iptables
    gzip

Suggested packages if building on a desktop machine:
    dbus
    libdbus-1-3
    libdbus-1-3-dev

How to build:
git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DNOPGLCMD=1 -DNOPGLGUI=1 ..
make
make install
##############################################################################

Installing only pglcmd:
git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DNOPGLD=1 -DNOPGLGUI=1 ..
make install

##############################################################################

Building only pgl-gui:

Required packages:
    Qt

git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DNOPGLD=1 -DNOPGLCMD=1 ..
make
make install

